org.apache.ctakes.ytex.uima.model

Class UimaType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.uima.model.UimaType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UimaType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Reference data. Defines YTEX uimaTypeID, uimaTypeName (Class name), and tableName. We need our own uima Type ID because the typeID field in the annotation is generated dynamically - it can change. Mapped to ref_uima_type.
